value: 2754 - Commercial Printing, Gravure Summary > GRAPHICS HOLDINGS AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover commercial printing, gravure. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. GRAPHICS HOLDINGS AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Minto, New South Wales. It is headed by director & company secretary Richard Leong. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.32 million. Its net profit totalled $1.20 million. GRAPHICS HOLDINGS AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the manufacturing industry sector.
